---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for NameGen Name Generator website."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#111111] dark:text-white">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888]">Last Updated: July 2, 2026</p>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Welcome to NameGen. By using our website, you agree to comply with the following Terms of Service.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#111111] dark:text-white mt-6">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing and using NameGen, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#111111] dark:text-white mt-6">2. Use of Generated Names</h2>
      <p>
        All names generated by this website are generated using open list assets and algorithms. We claim no ownership over the generated names. You are free to use them for commercial projects, writing, naming businesses, or gaming handles. However, we cannot guarantee that any name is free of existing trademark conflicts or copy-protection.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#111111] dark:text-white mt-6">3. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p>
        The site is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We do not guarantee that the name generator will meet all your requirements or be completely error-free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
